}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Sets the pipeline's ambient color, in the standard OpenGL lighting
model. The ambient color affects the overall color of the object.</p>  <p>Since the diffuse color will be intense when the light hits the surface
directly, the ambient will be most apparent where the light hits at a
slant.</p>  <p>The default value is (0.2, 0.2, 0.2, 1.0)</p>
  <p>Since 2.0</p>
